        "subject": "LU-858 build: check for generated autoconf.h header first",
        "message": "LU-858 build: check for generated autoconf.h header first\n\nFedora apparently provides a zero length autoconf.h in the standard\nlocation (for programs that might be testing for its presence?).\nHowever this causes the build scripts pre-include instead since it\nfinds that header file first.  Instead, check generated directory\nfirst for autoconf.h\n\nSigned-off-by: chas williams - CONTRACTOR <chas@cmf.nrl.navy.mil>\nChange-Id: I6ac590ce9bbc79d742c45e7638bc7c6c547bfe8d\n"
